data.description: Welcome to your rustic style home in the country! With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths and a 1,211 sq ft bonus area, there is room to spread out! The over sized primary with 2 closets is on the main level, as is the kitchen, dining area and living room. Downstairs is a huge laundry room, family room, 3 bedrooms and 2nd bathroom. This charming residence combines the tranquility of nature with the warmth of rustic design elements. The centerpiece of the living space is a cozy wood burning stove. The vaulted ceilings and wood beams add to the charm. One of the most remarkable features of this home is the expansive 1,500 sq ft wraparound covered enclosed patio. This versatile outdoor/indoor bonus space serves as an extension of the interior, allowing you to embrace the beauty of the outdoors while remaining sheltered from the elements. It's the perfect spot for hosting gatherings. Surrounded by 22 acres of natural beauty, the property provides endless opportunities for outdoor exploration and activities. The numerous fruit tress include red and yellow Delicious and Fuji apple tress, a pluot, cherry, and a dwarf orange tree. This property also has a whole house generator that turns on and off automatically, with an automatic transfer switch. Seller has an assumable VA loan at 2.8%
